message.field:
Positive or negative acknowledgment.
                // "1": MAV, which has received this message, got elected as replacement-MAV (replacement-MAV will receive all mission related data from the old MAV).
                //      The whole process is finished with REPLACEMENT_FINALIZE message.;
                // "0": MAV, which has received this message, will not be used as a replacement-MAV (the connection is closed immediately)
